15th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 11 Highlights

Stage 11 is 188km, starting in Pau and tackling two of the most iconic climbs in the Tour's history, the Col d'Aspin and the Col du Tourmalet, before finishing in the ski resort of Cauterets over 1500m above sea-level. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
